This image gathers the symbols used by the Brazilian Ministry of Justice to rate films, videogames, RPGs and TV shows. They are free to use, as long as credits are given to Secretaria Nacional de Justiça – Departamento de Justiça, Classificação, Títulos e Qualificação as stated here.
